{"tid":2062467,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【沙田】無懼警打壓 百人大合唱","createTime":"2020-06-13T07:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T07:05:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad61239440c6db11e746e51b60ee57a2e869f57","tid":2062467,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:01:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200613/OAPDATAYJSBVS2GU6UMM6S57RU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FOAPDATAYJSBVS2GU6UMM6S57RU%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJripZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=db1f2704\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FOAPDATAYJSBVS2GU6UMM6S57RU%2F&h=ee409bb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200613/OAPDATAYJSBVS2GU6UMM6S57RU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【沙田】無懼警打壓 百人大合唱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2DICDQ2J6LLQHBLW465YWZV7WQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2DICDQ2J6LLQHBLW465YWZV7WQ.jpg&h=9a9be4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民昨在新城市廣場籲堅持抗爭。&lt;br /&gt;翁志偉攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】過去多次發生防暴警暴力驅散抗爭者的沙田新城市廣場，昨晚再有數百名市民聚集，各人合唱反修例歌曲，亮起手機燈表達五大訴求。面對大批防暴警在商場外瘋狂截查，市民仍然堅持，有人在玻璃圍欄掛上「一息尚存，抗爭到底」標語，顯示民心不死。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：街站宣傳罷課 三學生被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防暴逼本報記者解鎖電話<br />\n<br />\n昨晚7時許，近百市民聚集在新城市廣場中庭，有人舉起「光復香港 時代革命」旗幟，晚上8時數百市民亮起手機燈合唱《願榮光歸香港》。區議員。。。。。。。。。。。。。。非常惡劣，更要求記者將公司電話解鎖。<br />\n<br />\n此外，昨晚8時有抗爭者在西寶城發起「和你dinner」，逾50名市民高唱《願榮光歸香港》。踏入8時09分市民低頭默哀，包括中西區區議員彭家浩及梁晃維。商場。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者趙媛媛、王靖琳"},{"pid":"e4b132f58057883bdaa0e6e6407b6e85a3a1879d","tid":2062467,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"我琴晚係灣仔道同 莊士敦道交界<br />\n<br />\n我估計大約有 40-60人， 另外仲有部份人係外圍叫。"}]}